get them out of my SIGHTS!" she barked. Getting rather irritated with the lot. 
It definitely took alot to irritate her. 

Now.. BACK to base.. ALL OF YOU!" 

She then turned to the Decepticon arrivals. "Follow us, you will receive 
repairs & energon at the base."
